# LRGSkyBlock-Core v0.7.0 Player Level Design

- Player Level XP requirement starts at 100 and increases by 50 every 40 levels.
- Every level-up grants +5 Health through the PLAYER_LEVEL stats layer.
- Every fifth level grants +1 Strength.
- Unlocks: Wardrobe Lv5, Auto Pickup Lv6, Bazaar Lv7, Accessory Bag Lv10.
- Accessory Bag expansion is reserved for Redstone Collection in v0.8.0.
- Auto Pickup sends block drops directly to inventory and drops only overflow at the block location.
- Vanilla experience is granted directly without spawning experience orbs.
- `/level` displays progress, unlocked/history entries, and level stat bonuses.
